    {
      "id": "Q1",
      "type": "single",
      "title": "若 $f(x) = e^{2x}$，則 $f'(x) = $？",
      "options": {
        "A": "$e^{2x}$",
        "B": "$2e^{2x}$",
        "C": "$\\frac{1}{2}e^{2x}$",
        "D": "$e^x$"
      },
      "answer": "B",
      "kp": "",
      "explanation": "根據連鎖律，$\\frac{d}{dx}(e^{u}) = e^u \\cdot u'$。令 $u = 2x$，則 $u' = 2$。故 $f'(x) = e^{2x} \\cdot 2 = 2e^{2x}$。",
      "q_vector": []
    },
    {
      "id": "Q2",
      "type": "single",
      "title": "$\\int \\frac{1}{x+1} dx = $？",
      "options": {
        "A": "$\\ln|x+1|+C$",
        "B": "$\\frac{1}{(x+1)^2}+C$",
        "C": "$e^{x+1}+C$",
        "D": "$x+C$"
      },
      "answer": "A",
      "kp": "",
      "explanation": "根據基本積分公式 $\\int \\frac{1}{u} du = \\ln|u| + C$。令 $u = x+1$，則 $du = dx$。原式 $= \\ln|x+1| + C$。",
      "q_vector": []
    },
    {
      "id": "Q3",
