      "q_vector": []
    },
    {
      "id": "Q4",
      "type": "single",
      "title": "函數 $y = \\log_{10} x$ 的導函數為？",
      "options": {
        "A": "$1/x$",
        "B": "$1/(x\\ln 10)$",
        "C": "$(\\ln 10)/x$",
        "D": "$10^x$"
      },
      "answer": "B",
      "kp": "",
      "explanation": "一般底數對數導函數公式為 $\\frac{d}{dx}(\\log_a x) = \\frac{1}{x \\ln a}$。此處 $a=10$，故為 $1/(x\\ln 10)$。",
      "q_vector": []
    },
    {
      "id": "Q5",
      "type": "single",
      "title": "若 $\\frac{dy}{dt} = 0.5y$ 且 $y(0)=10$，則 $y(2) = $？",
      "options": {
        "A": "$10e$",
        "B": "$10e^2$",
        "C": "$5e$",
        "D": "$10$"
      },
      "answer": "A",
      "kp": "",
      "explanation": "此為指數增長模型 $y(t) = y(0)e^{kt}$，其中 $k=0.5, y(0)=10$。則 $y(2) = 10e^{0.5 \\cdot 2} = 10e^1 = 10e$。",
      "q_vector": []
    },
